Di samping itu,

00:10:01.022 --> 00:10:03.262
Apakah menurutmu Pangeran Rui benar-benar menyukaimu?

00:10:03.262 --> 00:10:04.462
Dia peduli padamu

00:10:04.462 --> 00:10:06.782
