00:10:59.776 --> 00:11:05.344
Awan-awan yang kacau menghalangi
pandanganku yang penuh harap sekali lagi.

00:11:09.422 --> 00:11:10.742
Xiao Wenjing

00:11:10.742 --> 00:11:12.422
